member.name: M:Orleans.Streaming.AzureStorage.AzureBlobUtils.ContainerNameRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
^[a-z0-9]+(-[a-z0-9]+)*$
Options:
RegexOptions.ExplicitCapture | RegexOptions.Singleline | RegexOptions.CultureInvariant
Explanation:
○ Match if at the beginning of the string.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9a-z] greedily at least once.
○ Loop greedily any number of times.
○ Match '-'.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9a-z] atomically at least once.
○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.

○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.
